kButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juni 29, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104gsd1719644519908.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gsd1719644519908.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gsd1719644519908.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ysz1665702656946\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      /gly\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Compile glyphs.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ysz1665702656946__section_w1030ab1b5b1_w1031ab1b5_w1032ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ysz1665702656946__p_d149543e1_d149544e1_d149545e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/gly</span> {<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/aft=</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">DateTime</var>} {<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/bef=</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">DateTime</var>} {<var class=\"keyword varname\">Library</var>}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ysz1665702656946__section_w1033ab1b5b3_w1034ab1b5_w1035ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1073364e76\">\n                  \n Switches\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ysz1665702656946__d6084e20\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ide1665702625805.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ide1665702625805.html\" title=\"Compile objects modified after and/or before the date specified.\">/aft= or /bef=</a>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ysz1665702656946__section_w1036ab1b5b5_w1037ab1b5_w1038ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1073364e92\">\n                  \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ysz1665702656946__p_d149555e1_d149556e1_d149557e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Library</var>—name of the library containing the objects to compile; if omitted, all glyphs are compiled. Use wildcard characters to specify multiple libraries.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ysz1665702656946__section_w1039ab1b5b7_w1040ab1b5_w1041ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1073364e104\">\n                  \n Use With\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ysz1665702656946__d5931e20\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">ide.exe</span>—Uniface IDE</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ysz1665702656946__section_w1042ab1b5b9_w1043ab1b5_w1044ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1073364e116\"> Description </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ysz1665702656946__p_d149567e1_d149568e1_d149569e1\">The location of compiled glyphs is determined by\n            the $RSO path.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xfc1665702625593.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Compiling from the IDE Command Line</a><p>The IDE command line can be used to compile multiple objects without opening the IDE. It is especially useful for automating compilation by means of batch scripts.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nbf1705582294349.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Glyphs</a><p>Glyphs are images in a Uniface-proprietary format, which can be used as background images in forms, entities and application shells, and as icons in widgets, panel buttons, menus, and drag-and-drop formats.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7420974\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7420974\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "/gly Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juni 29, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 /gly Compile glyphs. /gly { /aft= DateTime } { /bef= DateTime } { Library } Switches /aft= or /bef= Parameters Library —name of the library containing the objects to compile; if omitted, all glyphs are compiled. Use wildcard characters to specify multiple libraries. Use With ide.exe —Uniface IDE Description The location of compiled glyphs is determined by the $RSO path. Related Links Compiling from the IDE Command Line The IDE command line can be used to compile multiple objects without opening the IDE. It is especially useful for automating compilation by means of batch scripts. Glyphs Glyphs are images in a Uniface-proprietary format, which can be used as background images in forms, entities and application shells, and as icons in widgets, panel buttons, menus, and drag-and-drop formats. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}